	    			<h2 class="headContent"> Protection </h2>
				<p class="tipContent"> To protect your self from
				the sun make sure to put on plenty of sunscreen
				and bring sunglasses and a hat for your trip. Also it is a good idea to put on bug spray.  
			When choosing a bug spray, you'll want to take in several factors when choosing a repellent. In general, you should think about
	    			how much time you will be spending outdoors. If you are planning to stay outside for a long time, it is recommended that you buy a bug spray
	    			that contains a higher concentration. On the other hand, you should buy a bug spray with lower concentration if you aren't planning to stay out long.  </p>
