				<p class="tipContent">Avoid hiking alone
				because the &quot;buddy system&quot; is safer during any
				type of activity. If traveling with a group,
				never stray from the group. If hiking alone,
				pick a well traveled trail. If you are going alone or with a group make sure you
				let someone know where you are going and when you should be expected to return.
 </p>
